{"tid":929019,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【用體重殺人】300磅女子發脾氣 坐落男友心口壓死佢","createTime":"2018-12-05T09:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T12:12:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3cfc5ba567e429a0ad798bb7dd87d3571f4772b8","tid":929019,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:37:23.000Z","msg":"美國賓夕凡尼亞州一名重300磅的女子喝醉後與男友爭執，她一氣之下坐在僅重120磅的男友胸口上令他窒息死亡；她承認三級謀殺罪，控方求刑18至36年。<br />\n案情指，44歲的托馬斯(Windi Thomas)今年3月18日在住所喝醉酒後欲買可卡因毒品，期間與同齡的男友巴特勒(Keeno Butler)爭執。重300磅的托馬斯起初用摺刀襲擊120磅的巴特勒，他的手受傷。托馬斯再用枱腳打他頭部，最後她更坐在其胸口上令他窒息死亡，她其後報警自首。<br />\n巴特勒的姊妹供稱，兩人拍拖兩年關係一向欠佳，認為托馬斯應判監40年或以上。案件押後至本月21日判刑。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181204/large/1543928286_36e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181204%2Flarge%2F1543928286_36e6.jpg&h=787dc574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3e157823374ec489a4b05ad0399700c7c32fd92","tid":929019,"uid":154212,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nteYnD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nteYnD.png&h=68953f0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7501d27024552c3cc3d0d83c0ef98e98cedf7405","tid":929019,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:39:11.000Z","msg":"catgirl<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25ccd3dc0551b82c292ef843eb20c2cfbdea420","tid":929019,"uid":142067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:40:28.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82562ceb271cd73701928bd5d5ea5f4adeb8c904","tid":929019,"uid":203945,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05